1
00:01:10,752 --> 00:01:12,431
=Those Days=

2
00:01:12,431 --> 00:01:14,800
(Adapted from iceread.com novel
"You Xi" by Qingyang Wanxi)

3
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:17,980
=Episode 25=

4
00:01:18,420 --> 00:01:18,900
Hu Gang,

5
00:01:19,260 --> 00:01:20,340
our home Wi-Fi is down.

6
00:01:20,460 --> 00:01:22,180
Our Al home system has collapsed.

7
00:01:22,580 --> 00:01:23,540
Please come and fix it.

8
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:27,820
That shouldn't be.

9
00:01:28,460 --> 00:01:30,340
I installed their Wi-Fi for them.

10
00:01:30,340 --> 00:01:32,650
I just installed it not long ago.
It shouldn't be possible.

11
00:01:32,660 --> 00:01:33,500
It malfunctioned, huh?

12
00:01:33,500 --> 00:01:35,180
Great timing.
Let's head there and fix it together.

13
00:01:35,180 --> 00:01:36,840
Is the commotion
not huge enough for you?

14
00:01:37,500 --> 00:01:39,300
Meiqi embarrassed me the entire day.

15
00:01:39,300 --> 00:01:40,660
She criticized me non-stop.

16
00:01:40,660 --> 00:01:44,020
I need to tell her that the bride is
the one paying me, not her, the bridesmaid.

17
00:01:44,020 --> 00:01:45,420
- Precisely.
- She shouldn't tell me what to do.

18
00:01:45,420 --> 00:01:47,700
If you go and argue with her,
you might get your revenge.

19
00:01:47,700 --> 00:01:48,980
But what about Bichen's wedding?

20
00:01:48,980 --> 00:01:49,780
What a joke.

21
00:01:49,780 --> 00:01:52,540
Who said Yuan Bichen
couldn't get married without Feng Meiqi?

22
00:01:52,540 --> 00:01:54,540
Today, I'm going to show her
who's the boss.

23
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:55,540
What do you think?

24
00:01:55,540 --> 00:01:56,780
Enough. You shouldn't.

25
00:01:56,780 --> 00:01:58,290
I want to show her who's the boss here.

26
00:01:58,300 --> 00:01:58,860
Bring it on.

27
00:02:01,580 --> 00:02:02,260
Meiqi?

28
00:02:04,020 --> 00:02:04,740
Show me, then.

29
00:02:06,420 --> 00:02:07,380
So, you haven't left.

30
00:02:12,210 --> 00:02:14,710
How could I enjoy this fantastic show
if I left early just now?

31
00:02:22,580 --> 00:02:23,300
Hu Gang.

32
00:02:25,460 --> 00:02:26,740
My mother always said

33
00:02:28,220 --> 00:02:30,740
that you were honest and trustworthy.

34
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:35,020
Is being fickle-minded
considered honest?

35
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,540
That's not it.

36
00:02:36,540 --> 00:02:38,460
Is being fickle-minded
considered trustworthy?

37
00:02:38,660 --> 00:02:40,180
No, that's not it.

38
00:02:40,180 --> 00:02:40,780
You see...

39
00:02:41,180 --> 00:02:43,140
Back then, you told me

40
00:02:43,380 --> 00:02:45,140
not to find you again.

41
00:02:45,140 --> 00:02:45,820
I...

42
00:02:45,820 --> 00:02:47,500
Bichen even wanted to break up
with Xu Zhidong, you know?

43
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:48,420
She even wanted an abortion!

44
00:02:48,420 --> 00:02:49,540
Even so,
their relationship is still fine!

45
00:02:49,540 --> 00:02:50,860
They're even getting married now.

46
00:02:51,020 --> 00:02:51,740
Calm down.

47
00:02:51,740 --> 00:02:52,940
Don't touch me!

48
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:55,500
You found out long ago, didn't you?

49
00:02:56,050 --> 00:02:57,180
You didn't tell me on purpose

50
00:02:57,180 --> 00:02:58,740
just so you could mock me, did you?

51
00:02:58,740 --> 00:03:00,180
Meiqi, don't say that.

52
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:01,180
Go away!

53
00:03:01,820 --> 00:03:02,460
And you.

54
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,940
You're Shen Mingzhu's bosom friend.

55
00:03:04,940 --> 00:03:06,460
I'm sure you know about
my relationship with Hu Gang.

56
00:03:06,460 --> 00:03:07,460
What do you mean by this?

57
00:03:07,980 --> 00:03:09,220
Did you do this on purpose?

58
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:12,580
Feng Meiqi, you're so twisted
you're practically a joke.

59
00:03:12,580 --> 00:03:14,050
People mocking you
should be normal to you.

60
00:03:14,580 --> 00:03:15,220
Stop it.

61
00:03:15,220 --> 00:03:15,660
Come.

62
00:03:15,660 --> 00:03:16,860
Pregnant girl, go away.

63
00:03:16,860 --> 00:03:18,140
Let's try to reason this out.

64
00:03:18,540 --> 00:03:19,540
Hu Gang did court you,

65
00:03:19,580 --> 00:03:20,660
but did you say yes to him?

66
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,900
When Hu Gang offended you,
did you forgive him?

67
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,860
When Hu Gang did
all those things for you,

68
00:03:25,860 --> 00:03:27,100
have you ever thanked him before?

69
00:03:27,100 --> 00:03:27,940
Don't bring that up.

70
00:03:27,940 --> 00:03:28,620
Go away.

71
00:03:29,100 --> 00:03:31,220
Feng Meiqi, do you truly think
that you're a princess

72
00:03:31,220 --> 00:03:33,100
and the world revolves around you?

73
00:03:33,100 --> 00:03:35,420
Do you even know the word "respect"?

74
00:03:35,500 --> 00:03:37,060
Do you know how to respect other people?

75
00:03:37,060 --> 00:03:39,540
If you lack a loyal and obedient lackey,
get yourself a dog.

76
00:03:39,540 --> 00:03:40,940
It'll wag its tail
in front of you all day long.

77
00:03:40,940 --> 00:03:42,300
And, it'll never retaliate
even if you hurt it.

78
00:03:42,300 --> 00:03:43,220
It'll be loyal to you forever.

79
00:03:43,220 --> 00:03:44,890
Hu Gang,
was that your true thought all along?

80
00:03:44,900 --> 00:03:46,100
Was it true?

81
00:03:46,100 --> 00:03:47,620
That's not it. I'm sorry.

82
00:03:47,620 --> 00:03:48,700
- Who said I wanted your apology?
- That's not true.

83
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:49,820
Why are you apologizing to her?

84
00:03:49,820 --> 00:03:50,380
Meiqi,

85
00:03:50,380 --> 00:03:51,460
let me send you home, okay?

86
00:03:51,460 --> 00:03:52,580
What are you saying?

87
00:03:53,980 --> 00:03:55,580
I don't even have a home!

88
00:03:56,220 --> 00:03:58,140
Shen Mingzhu, you're my sister-in-law.

89
00:03:58,140 --> 00:04:00,260
Is this how you treat me
after my brother's passing?

90
00:04:03,980 --> 00:04:04,660
Hu Gang,

91
00:04:06,220 --> 00:04:07,060
I'll remember this.

92
00:04:09,780 --> 00:04:10,380
Meiqi!

93
00:04:10,380 --> 00:04:10,860
You...

94
00:04:11,180 --> 00:04:12,100
Lend me your car.

95
00:04:12,100 --> 00:04:13,060
Hurry, hand me the keys.

96
00:04:13,060 --> 00:04:14,060
It's in the bag.

97
00:04:14,180 --> 00:04:15,180
It's in the bag.

98
00:04:19,710 --> 00:04:20,820
- That lass...
- Slow down.

99
00:04:20,820 --> 00:04:21,740
Be careful. You're pregnant.

100
00:04:21,740 --> 00:04:22,580
Slow down.

101
00:04:23,180 --> 00:04:23,900
Meiqi!

102
00:04:35,660 --> 00:04:36,340
Meiqi.

103
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:38,500
You don't depend on another person

104
00:04:39,700 --> 00:04:40,940
to lead the life you want.

105
00:04:41,940 --> 00:04:43,300
You depend on yourself.

106
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:47,500
It doesn't matter if you give
Mr. Hu your blessings or not.

107
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:50,860
(Grave of Feng Jianqi)
You need to learn how to accept reality.

108
00:04:52,140 --> 00:04:54,380
How can I live on

109
00:04:54,460 --> 00:04:56,340
if I still dwell on
Jianqi's passing every day?

110
00:05:21,500 --> 00:05:23,580
But I miss him so much!

111
00:05:25,220 --> 00:05:26,220
I miss him too.

112
00:05:30,860 --> 00:05:33,660
Jianqi was the kindest person
in the world to me!

113
00:05:34,900 --> 00:05:37,060
But he's gone!

114
00:05:39,340 --> 00:05:40,740
You still have your parents.

115
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:42,740
You still have us.

116
00:05:51,460 --> 00:05:53,860
I think I didn't handle this matter

117
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:57,300
appropriately.

118
00:05:57,780 --> 00:05:58,900
Which part?

119
00:05:59,540 --> 00:06:00,840
Now that we're in a relationship,

120
00:06:02,340 --> 00:06:03,620
I think I should

121
00:06:05,180 --> 00:06:06,060
tell her about it.

122
00:06:09,750 --> 00:06:10,820
I know you courted Meiqi.

123
00:06:11,220 --> 00:06:13,280
But did she admit
that you were her boyfriend?

124
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:15,350
And, why do you need
to report yourself to her

125
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:17,260
just because
you're in a relationship with me?

126
00:06:19,660 --> 00:06:21,980
I think that's unnecessary.

127
00:06:22,180 --> 00:06:23,380
Yeah. That's it, then.

128
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:24,660
Hello. Please enjoy your meal.

129
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:25,380
Thank you.

130
00:06:25,380 --> 00:06:26,420
Come, hand the bowl to me.

131
00:06:27,460 --> 00:06:30,380
In life, it's all about eating
and drinking well.

132
00:06:36,980 --> 00:06:37,420
Ni,

133
00:06:38,860 --> 00:06:41,580
you don't seem
to have any worries, do you?

134
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,460
I don't have any worries?

135
00:06:43,460 --> 00:06:44,950
You'll be shocked
when I tell you about them.

136
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:47,260
But they'll be gone
as long as I don't think about them.

137
00:06:49,260 --> 00:06:50,440
You have such a great personality.

138
00:06:50,980 --> 00:06:51,780
Unlike me.

139
00:06:51,820 --> 00:06:52,620
When I was young,

140
00:06:52,620 --> 00:06:54,780
even if I flunked just one subject,

141
00:06:55,100 --> 00:06:56,620
I would dwell on it every day.

142
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:58,130
I would think about
this saying every day,

143
00:06:58,140 --> 00:06:59,940
"Learning without reflection
is meaningless.

144
00:06:59,940 --> 00:07:01,660
Reflection without learning
is dangerous".

145
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:04,820
If so, you should learn from
Luo Yin's example.

146
00:07:05,340 --> 00:07:07,020
"Drink today's wine and be drunk today,

147
00:07:07,380 --> 00:07:09,620
let tomorrow's sorrow
come with tomorrow".

148
00:07:09,860 --> 00:07:10,500
Don't you agree?

149
00:07:10,660 --> 00:07:10,940
Here.

150
00:07:18,620 --> 00:07:21,820
Actually, I knew about
your relationship with Meiqi long ago.

151
00:07:22,450 --> 00:07:24,180
I always wanted
to uphold justice for you.

152
00:07:25,220 --> 00:07:26,660
I think you're a nice guy.

153
00:07:26,670 --> 00:07:29,050
And, you shouldn't play the role
of a dog in a relationship.

154
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:31,220
But you couldn't curb your passion,

155
00:07:31,220 --> 00:07:32,220
and you did it willingly.

156
00:07:33,020 --> 00:07:34,900
Therefore, I could only
shake my head and sigh.

157
00:07:35,060 --> 00:07:36,580
I couldn't do anything to help you out.

158
00:07:38,940 --> 00:07:39,740
But why?

159
00:07:39,740 --> 00:07:41,140
I have my own principles.

160
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:43,520
I can snag a bargain,
but I won't resort to outright theft.

161
00:07:45,460 --> 00:07:47,900
Therefore, I only found an opportunity
when there was a crack

162
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:49,250
between your relationship with her.

163
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,980
But to be honest,
I did set up an elaborate plot.

164
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:55,700
Delivering meals to you,
pretending to be sick,

165
00:07:55,700 --> 00:07:57,300
all those were parts of my plot.

166
00:07:57,700 --> 00:07:59,740
I've been really good
at this since young.

167
00:08:01,820 --> 00:08:02,460
If so,

168
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:03,980
you...

169
00:08:03,980 --> 00:08:05,850
You think that I've used Meiqi
to my advantage?

170
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:10,510
Why didn't it occur to you
that Meiqi was using you instead?

171
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:13,260
You provided free labor, and you followed
every one of her commands.

172
00:08:14,740 --> 00:08:17,420
I was merely lifting a finger.

173
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:19,260
So, you did it willingly.

174
00:08:21,460 --> 00:08:23,180
If so, are you
still willing to do it now?

175
00:08:25,860 --> 00:08:26,660
Tell me why.

176
00:08:35,980 --> 00:08:37,620
It's because you were
treated with kindness.

177
00:08:37,620 --> 00:08:38,980
You no longer want to be a suck-up.

178
00:08:38,980 --> 00:08:39,220
I...

179
00:08:40,100 --> 00:08:41,020
I wasn't a suck-up.

180
00:08:42,660 --> 00:08:43,740
Let me ask you this, then.

181
00:08:44,380 --> 00:08:45,820
What if I didn't exist?

182
00:08:46,020 --> 00:08:48,450
Do you think you can maintain
a good relationship with Meiqi?

183
00:08:50,500 --> 00:08:50,940
No.

184
00:08:50,940 --> 00:08:52,040
That's all there is to it.

185
00:08:52,940 --> 00:08:55,100
Since that's the case,
only fools wouldn't pick me.

186
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:56,900
C is always the best answer if there
are three long and one short answer.

187
00:08:56,900 --> 00:08:57,780
I'm C.

188
00:08:57,780 --> 00:08:59,320
You don't even need to know the answer.

189
00:08:59,940 --> 00:09:00,700
Mr. Hu,

190
00:09:00,940 --> 00:09:04,260
you see, the most important thing
in life is to be happy.

191
00:09:05,140 --> 00:09:06,340
Understood?

192
00:09:07,020 --> 00:09:07,820
Understood.

193
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:09,940
The most important thing
in life is to be happy.

194
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:11,350
- Understood.
- Let's dig in.

195
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:17,700
Can you be nice when we get back?

196
00:09:21,860 --> 00:09:23,380
Alright. I'll go and return the car.

197
00:09:30,020 --> 00:09:30,780
Listen,

198
00:09:30,780 --> 00:09:32,540
I watched a short drama a few days ago.

199
00:09:32,540 --> 00:09:33,500
It was terrifying.

200
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:35,100
You're back.

201
00:09:35,940 --> 00:09:37,140
The princess is back.

202
00:09:37,940 --> 00:09:40,540
Come, sit here with us.

203
00:09:40,540 --> 00:09:42,020
I even had nightmares about it.

204
00:09:43,260 --> 00:09:44,380
What's wrong?

205
00:09:46,260 --> 00:09:47,820
Why do you look so listless?

206
00:09:48,500 --> 00:09:49,180
Let me see.

207
00:09:49,580 --> 00:09:50,580
Who bullied you?

208
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:52,260
Tell me. I'll beat him up.

209
00:09:52,300 --> 00:09:54,300
Who do you think you can beat up?

210
00:09:54,300 --> 00:09:54,780
I'll.

211
00:09:55,620 --> 00:09:56,260
It's you.

212
00:09:56,900 --> 00:09:57,540
Me?

213
00:09:58,020 --> 00:09:59,180
But I didn't provoke you.

214
00:10:00,660 --> 00:10:03,060
I told you to top up
our hotel's VIP card, but you didn't.

215
00:10:03,060 --> 00:10:03,660
Great.

216
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:05,350
My superiors told me off
because of that.

217
00:10:06,060 --> 00:10:07,900
That's it?
Do they even need to go that far?

218
00:10:08,180 --> 00:10:08,940
Yeah.

219
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,460
That's right. Top up your card.

220
00:10:11,060 --> 00:10:11,940
I've permitted it.

221
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,380
Tell your father to top up the card.

222
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:15,820
You need to use it
when you entertain guests anyway.

223
00:10:15,820 --> 00:10:16,950
You should help our daughter out.

224
00:10:17,060 --> 00:10:17,700
Mrs. Feng,

225
00:10:17,940 --> 00:10:19,340
the soup ingredients are ready.

226
00:10:19,500 --> 00:10:20,820
Please come and take a look.

227
00:10:20,820 --> 00:10:23,180
Please check whether I've followed
your exact procedures.

228
00:10:23,180 --> 00:10:24,460
Alright. Coming.

229
00:10:25,260 --> 00:10:26,220
Lass,

230
00:10:27,100 --> 00:10:28,860
how many times have I told you already?

231
00:10:29,980 --> 00:10:31,860
Don't wait around for things to happen.

232
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:34,480
You need to resolve the issues you face
with your own abilities.

233
00:10:35,060 --> 00:10:37,220
You come looking for me
whenever you face an issue.

234
00:10:37,980 --> 00:10:39,220
What if one day I...

235
00:10:40,060 --> 00:10:41,120
What will you do by then?

236
00:10:41,140 --> 00:10:42,060
No way!

237
00:10:43,140 --> 00:10:44,620
Dad, you have to be around forever.

238
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:46,740
You have to live a long life.

239
00:10:46,940 --> 00:10:49,940
Alright.
I hope your blessing will come true.

240
00:10:50,700 --> 00:10:52,380
But I'm speaking the truth.

241
00:10:53,620 --> 00:10:54,580
But Feng,

242
00:10:55,620 --> 00:10:56,740
you can't just do this.

243
00:10:57,660 --> 00:10:59,100
Whenever we talk about Mingzhu,

244
00:10:59,100 --> 00:11:00,060
you talk about unity.

245
00:11:00,060 --> 00:11:02,310
But when it's my turn,
you talk about being independent.

246
00:11:03,060 --> 00:11:04,820
I knew you were going to bring that up.

247
00:11:05,560 --> 00:11:08,300
This time, I didn't top up the card
I used in Mingzhu's hotel either.

248
00:11:09,380 --> 00:11:11,380
I wasn't partial at all.

249
00:11:11,380 --> 00:11:12,780
I'm fair to everyone.

250
00:11:14,420 --> 00:11:15,460
As if.

251
00:11:18,260 --> 00:11:19,540
Next time, when you come back,

252
00:11:20,100 --> 00:11:21,500
you mustn't pull a long face.

253
00:11:21,820 --> 00:11:25,180
You must smile when you see us.

254
00:11:25,300 --> 00:11:26,260
Isn't that great?

255
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:28,940
That's it.

256
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,250
Look at how beautiful my girl is.

257
00:11:37,340 --> 00:11:38,180
Don't worry.

258
00:11:38,340 --> 00:11:40,460
Meiqi has become calmer
after returning home.

259
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:41,620
She should be fine.

260
00:11:41,860 --> 00:11:42,820
I knew it.

261
00:11:43,060 --> 00:11:44,220
People are just like clay.

262
00:11:44,220 --> 00:11:46,350
The more you mold them,
the more resilient they become.

263
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:48,420
You're quite concerned
about her, aren't you?

264
00:11:49,060 --> 00:11:50,700
Why don't you offer Mr. Hu to her again?

265
00:11:50,860 --> 00:11:51,700
What a joke.

266
00:11:51,820 --> 00:11:53,460
Do you think I get to make the call?

267
00:11:53,460 --> 00:11:55,360
You have to ask Mr. Hu
for his permission first.

268
00:11:55,740 --> 00:11:57,740
I just think
that the lass has a rough time.

269
00:11:58,060 --> 00:11:59,950
She's in eloquent,
yet she has a fragile heart.

270
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:01,250
She doesn't know how to love people
when she wants to.

271
00:12:01,260 --> 00:12:03,340
And, she doesn't know how to
return the favor after being loved.

272
00:12:03,980 --> 00:12:05,550
Perhaps she'll understand in the future.

273
00:12:07,010 --> 00:12:09,950
In the past, it never occurred to me
how I should live as a single mother.

274
00:12:10,020 --> 00:12:12,220
But look, my baby is this big now.

275
00:12:13,820 --> 00:12:14,900
(Shocking Price for Gold)
Your belly,

276
00:12:14,980 --> 00:12:16,820
has it gotten bigger again?

277
00:12:16,820 --> 00:12:18,500
He's growing up at a rapid rate.

278
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:21,020
Dear baby, you're lucky.

279
00:12:21,020 --> 00:12:23,140
Your mother is going
to buy gold bars for you again.

280
00:12:24,620 --> 00:12:25,180
Let's go.

281
00:12:27,460 --> 00:12:28,100
Hello.

282
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:30,140
Hello. What would you
like to buy this time?

283
00:12:30,300 --> 00:12:32,220
The timeless gold bars.

284
00:12:32,220 --> 00:12:32,820
Alright.

285
00:12:34,580 --> 00:12:35,900
I want this, Peace and Fortune.

286
00:12:40,820 --> 00:12:41,820
Alright. Here you go.

287
00:12:41,900 --> 00:12:42,500
Okay.

288
00:12:44,560 --> 00:12:45,740
Are you buying this next time?

289
00:12:46,020 --> 00:12:47,700
I'll buy all of them
when I'm rich enough.

290
00:12:48,380 --> 00:12:49,860
Aunt Ni, why don't you sponsor us?

291
00:12:50,660 --> 00:12:51,900
No can do.

292
00:12:54,380 --> 00:12:56,700
Look at our generous baby.

293
00:13:06,420 --> 00:13:07,420
Hello, Mr. Zhang?

294
00:13:08,380 --> 00:13:10,540
I'm Meiqi from Lijun Hotel.

295
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:13,780
I was wondering how you and your wife
were getting on with your plans.

296
00:13:13,780 --> 00:13:15,180
We would be delighted

297
00:13:15,180 --> 00:13:16,840
to host your son's
100th day celebration.

298
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:22,340
Oh, you're hosting it
at Manjianghong Hotel?

299
00:13:24,540 --> 00:13:25,140
That's okay.

300
00:13:25,140 --> 00:13:26,820
I hope we have the chance to serve you

301
00:13:26,820 --> 00:13:28,180
in the future.

302
00:13:29,460 --> 00:13:31,340
May your baby grow strong and healthy.

303
00:13:31,980 --> 00:13:32,700
Okay.

304
00:13:33,100 --> 00:13:33,540
Goodbye.

305
00:13:39,380 --> 00:13:41,540
My mother made this beef sauce for you.

306
00:13:41,580 --> 00:13:42,980
It contains black wolf berries.

307
00:13:42,980 --> 00:13:44,100
Oh yeah, there's this too.

308
00:13:44,420 --> 00:13:45,700
And this paper bag as well.

309
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:46,760
It's dried bamboo shoots.

310
00:13:46,780 --> 00:13:48,540
Cook them with roasted pork,
and you'll be in for a treat.

311
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:50,100
How can I finish them all?

312
00:13:50,100 --> 00:13:50,740
You can do it.

313
00:13:50,740 --> 00:13:51,740
Please help me thank...

314
00:13:52,220 --> 00:13:53,450
Thank your mother on my behalf.

315
00:13:54,460 --> 00:13:55,820
How is she doing?

316
00:13:55,820 --> 00:13:57,300
She's doing great.

317
00:13:57,540 --> 00:13:58,620
You may not know,

318
00:13:58,740 --> 00:14:00,700
but she's busy every day.

319
00:14:00,700 --> 00:14:02,380
She prepares three sets of everything.

320
00:14:02,380 --> 00:14:04,220
She's energetic way beyond her age.

321
00:14:04,340 --> 00:14:05,540
If we were in the ancient era,

322
00:14:05,540 --> 00:14:08,120
I suppose she could've joined
the military on Xu Zhidong's behalf.

323
00:14:12,020 --> 00:14:12,620
So,

324
00:14:13,340 --> 00:14:15,700
regarding my husband's selection,

325
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:17,950
have you received any news
from your father-in-law?

326
00:14:18,100 --> 00:14:18,780
Not yet.

327
00:14:21,340 --> 00:14:23,500
What about this? I'll head back
and ask him about it.

328
00:14:24,980 --> 00:14:25,660
Mingzhu,

329
00:14:26,100 --> 00:14:29,140
I know it's difficult for you
to ask for a favor there.

330
00:14:29,540 --> 00:14:30,940
I must've troubled you.

331
00:14:30,940 --> 00:14:31,820
I'm so sorry about this.

332
00:14:31,820 --> 00:14:32,660
It's fine.

333
00:14:32,940 --> 00:14:34,700
I only told my father-in-law about it.

334
00:14:34,700 --> 00:14:35,940
My mother-in-law has no idea.

335
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:37,420
I'm glad that it's not troubling you.

336
00:14:37,420 --> 00:14:38,060
Not at all.

337
00:14:38,980 --> 00:14:40,780
If Zhang Hao is promoted,

338
00:14:40,780 --> 00:14:42,580
he'll make an extra 10k or 20k per year.

339
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:45,920
You'll make the same amount
if you just publish a few more posts.

340
00:14:46,060 --> 00:14:47,340
My dear sister,

341
00:14:48,980 --> 00:14:51,340
you have no idea
how difficult it is to make money now.

342
00:14:51,620 --> 00:14:53,820
Official accounts
are popping up everywhere.

343
00:14:53,820 --> 00:14:55,260
Whenever there's a hot piece of news,

344
00:14:55,460 --> 00:14:57,420
people will write about it
from every angle.

345
00:14:57,420 --> 00:14:59,620
It's truly difficult for me
to gain attention.

346
00:15:00,460 --> 00:15:03,020
If your posts don't get many clicks,
they won't generate ad revenues.

347
00:15:03,020 --> 00:15:04,580
Without ads,
there's no way to make money.

348
00:15:04,580 --> 00:15:06,740
If there's no money,
I have to pay for it with my own.

349
00:15:07,180 --> 00:15:08,340
I have to pay the office rent,

350
00:15:08,340 --> 00:15:09,900
utility bills, management fees...

351
00:15:10,340 --> 00:15:12,220
Oh yeah, and the wage of
my personal assistant.

352
00:15:12,220 --> 00:15:13,580
I have to pay all of that.

353
00:15:14,300 --> 00:15:16,100
Whenever I think about these bills,

354
00:15:16,220 --> 00:15:17,660
I can't sleep at night.

355
00:15:17,820 --> 00:15:19,820
It makes my hair fall out in clumps.

356
00:15:19,820 --> 00:15:20,460
Is that so?

357
00:15:21,340 --> 00:15:22,980
I suppose you have a lot of hair, then.

358
00:15:25,260 --> 00:15:26,380
It must've been tough.

359
00:15:27,140 --> 00:15:27,980
Forget about

360
00:15:27,980 --> 00:15:29,860
this tiny studio of ours.

361
00:15:30,580 --> 00:15:33,540
Even those big-time clients

362
00:15:33,660 --> 00:15:35,580
who've sailed smoothly for decades

363
00:15:35,580 --> 00:15:37,460
will be knocked off their feet
by a single wave,

364
00:15:37,460 --> 00:15:37,980
you know?

365
00:15:37,980 --> 00:15:39,660
Such examples are everywhere.

366
00:15:41,560 --> 00:15:42,420
I have to stop here.

367
00:15:42,420 --> 00:15:43,690
I need to visit the F&B Department.

368
00:15:43,700 --> 00:15:45,060
Someone complained about Rufeng Liquor.

369
00:15:45,060 --> 00:15:46,420
I have to help
the suppliers deal with it.

370
00:15:46,420 --> 00:15:47,620
Is that included
in your job scope as well?

371
00:15:47,820 --> 00:15:49,950
Didn't I tell you already?
It's difficult to make money nowadays.

372
00:15:52,160 --> 00:15:53,940
I have to make sure
I provide good services

373
00:15:53,940 --> 00:15:55,330
to my clients
while I can still move around.

374
00:15:55,340 --> 00:15:57,220
I'm going to keep every penny I earn

375
00:15:57,220 --> 00:15:58,980
firmly in my own hands.

376
00:15:59,260 --> 00:15:59,940
Let me join you.

377
00:15:59,940 --> 00:16:01,560
- It's fine. Just resume your work.
- This is troublesome indeed.

378
00:16:01,570 --> 00:16:02,860
Sorry that you have
to come here personally.

379
00:16:02,860 --> 00:16:03,580
Mr. Ding.

380
00:16:03,740 --> 00:16:06,380
All those alcoholics love to cause trouble
after getting drunk.

381
00:16:07,220 --> 00:16:08,260
But to us,

382
00:16:08,260 --> 00:16:09,580
the customer is always right.

383
00:16:10,100 --> 00:16:11,100
Please bear with it.

384
00:16:11,500 --> 00:16:12,660
No problem.

385
00:16:12,740 --> 00:16:14,020
Let's discuss this in the office.

386
00:16:14,360 --> 00:16:16,700
By the way, Mr. Feng has used up
all the money on his card.

387
00:16:16,900 --> 00:16:18,540
And now, he owes us a few thousand yuan.

388
00:16:18,580 --> 00:16:20,420
You know this too.
Business is hard nowadays.

389
00:16:20,500 --> 00:16:21,580
Please tell him about it later.

390
00:16:21,580 --> 00:16:23,140
That's fine. I'll pay it off after this.

391
00:16:23,220 --> 00:16:24,260
There's no rush.

392
00:16:24,740 --> 00:16:25,700
It just occurred to me.

393
00:16:25,700 --> 00:16:26,740
That's why I told you.

394
00:16:26,740 --> 00:16:27,380
It'll be fine.

395
00:16:27,460 --> 00:16:28,860
I'll ask him to reimburse me later.

396
00:16:28,860 --> 00:16:30,180
Okay. Let's go, then.

397
00:16:30,180 --> 00:16:30,700
I'll make a move now.

398
00:16:30,700 --> 00:16:31,650
Okay. You guys can go ahead.

399
00:16:31,660 --> 00:16:32,580
Come. Over here.

400
00:16:35,700 --> 00:16:36,300
What?

401
00:16:37,340 --> 00:16:38,020
I owe them money?

402
00:16:39,420 --> 00:16:41,300
So, how much have you paid
on my behalf?

403
00:16:41,820 --> 00:16:42,780
3,500 yuan.

404
00:16:42,790 --> 00:16:44,620
Okay. Sorry about that.
I'll transfer the money to you now.

405
00:16:44,620 --> 00:16:46,220
Dad, it's fine. There's no rush.

406
00:16:46,220 --> 00:16:47,300
I'm so forgetful now.

407
00:16:49,940 --> 00:16:51,260
(Balance)

408
00:16:55,540 --> 00:16:56,860
What was my password again?

409
00:16:56,860 --> 00:16:58,220
I can't remember it.

410
00:16:58,220 --> 00:16:58,940
Dad, it's fine.

411
00:16:58,940 --> 00:17:00,160
You don't need to pay me back.

412
00:17:00,260 --> 00:17:01,100
Don't worry.

413
00:17:01,110 --> 00:17:02,020
I'll transfer it to you later.

414
00:17:02,020 --> 00:17:03,460
It's fine. You don't need to pay me.

415
00:17:08,220 --> 00:17:08,700
Lihua.

416
00:17:09,580 --> 00:17:10,060
Lihua?

417
00:17:10,660 --> 00:17:11,820
I need to tell you something.

418
00:17:11,940 --> 00:17:12,580
What's wrong?

419
00:17:13,980 --> 00:17:16,700
Transfer 3,500 yuan to Mingzhu.

420
00:17:16,980 --> 00:17:17,700
For what?

421
00:17:17,760 --> 00:17:19,500
Why should I transfer the money to her?
Why aren't you doing it?

422
00:17:19,500 --> 00:17:20,960
I didn't bring that much money with me

423
00:17:20,960 --> 00:17:22,140
when I went to their hotel last time.

424
00:17:22,140 --> 00:17:23,370
Mingzhu paid off
the balance on my behalf.

425
00:17:23,380 --> 00:17:23,900
Transfer the money to her.

426
00:17:23,900 --> 00:17:25,740
I'll transfer it to you
when I come back from work.

427
00:17:27,860 --> 00:17:29,700
You see, I forgot my password.

428
00:17:29,700 --> 00:17:31,140
It's all because you drink too much.

429
00:17:31,140 --> 00:17:32,460
You even forgot about your password.

430
00:17:32,460 --> 00:17:33,140
Keep on drinking,

431
00:17:33,140 --> 00:17:34,580
and you'll grow senile.

432
00:17:35,360 --> 00:17:36,860
I'll transfer the money to her later.

433
00:17:42,620 --> 00:17:45,460
Even those big-time clients

434
00:17:45,700 --> 00:17:47,460
who've sailed smoothly for decades

435
00:17:47,460 --> 00:17:49,420
will be knocked off their feet
by a single wave,

436
00:17:49,420 --> 00:17:49,940
you know?

437
00:17:49,940 --> 00:17:51,540
Such examples are everywhere.

438
00:17:51,540 --> 00:17:52,340
(Usable Balance)

439
00:18:29,060 --> 00:18:29,820
(Jianqi,)

440
00:18:30,460 --> 00:18:32,620
(I'm going to secure
this house for my baby.)

441
00:18:33,140 --> 00:18:34,380
(Will you blame me for this?)

442
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:37,180
(I'm going to do it even if
you're blaming me for it.)

443
00:18:37,380 --> 00:18:38,700
(It's because I'm a mother.)

444
00:18:45,380 --> 00:18:46,300
Are you saying

445
00:18:47,120 --> 00:18:49,350
that you want to transfer
the ownership of this marital house?

446
00:18:51,060 --> 00:18:53,620
This unit is registered
under Jianqi's name.

447
00:18:54,500 --> 00:18:56,060
When Jianqi left,

448
00:18:56,540 --> 00:18:57,660
you guys promised me

449
00:18:57,940 --> 00:18:59,420
that I would own this house

450
00:19:00,060 --> 00:19:01,620
once I gave birth to your grandchild.

451
00:19:02,700 --> 00:19:04,340
Back then, I didn't think much about it.

452
00:19:04,750 --> 00:19:06,620
But now, my belly is
growing bigger and bigger.

453
00:19:06,760 --> 00:19:08,860
I won't be able
to move around freely in the future.

454
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:11,160
Therefore, I want to transfer
the ownership of the house

455
00:19:11,580 --> 00:19:12,860
while I can still move around.

456
00:19:15,100 --> 00:19:17,100
I'm sure your parents
gave you that idea.

457
00:19:17,940 --> 00:19:19,340
No, it's my idea.

458
00:19:21,580 --> 00:19:24,060
The title deed is in Jianqi's name.

459
00:19:24,060 --> 00:19:27,020
It'll be troublesome
to do an ownership transfer.

460
00:19:27,020 --> 00:19:27,860
It's not.

461
00:19:28,060 --> 00:19:29,280
I've already inquired about it.

462
00:19:29,290 --> 00:19:30,850
I just need to get a notarized document

463
00:19:31,300 --> 00:19:33,940
stating that you and Dad
will relinquish the inheritance right.

464
00:19:37,780 --> 00:19:39,300
It's not like my parents will scam you.

465
00:19:39,580 --> 00:19:40,860
Why are you getting it notarized?

466
00:19:41,660 --> 00:19:42,420
Precisely.

467
00:19:43,900 --> 00:19:45,340
We're a family.

468
00:19:46,420 --> 00:19:49,020
We will keep our promise.

469
00:19:49,500 --> 00:19:50,140
Besides,

470
00:19:50,940 --> 00:19:52,700
the title deed is in Jianqi's name.

471
00:19:52,700 --> 00:19:54,260
That means the house is yours.

472
00:19:55,700 --> 00:19:57,540
The house isn't mine

473
00:19:58,180 --> 00:19:59,950
as long as the title deed
isn't in my name.

474
00:20:03,900 --> 00:20:06,860
But what if you get remarried?

475
00:20:07,380 --> 00:20:08,700
This is pre-marital property.

476
00:20:09,100 --> 00:20:11,340
I'm securing it for my child.

477
00:20:12,060 --> 00:20:13,420
Once I give birth to my child,

478
00:20:13,430 --> 00:20:15,060
I'll include his name in the title deed.

479
00:20:16,080 --> 00:20:17,780
If so, you can just add
the child's name to the title deed

480
00:20:17,780 --> 00:20:19,500
once he's born.

481
00:20:20,180 --> 00:20:21,450
Why go through all that trouble?

482
00:20:22,180 --> 00:20:24,180
What about my interest as his mother?

483
00:20:24,710 --> 00:20:27,420
Did you decide to give birth to a child
only because of the interest?

484
00:20:30,420 --> 00:20:32,180
I decided to have a child first.

485
00:20:32,820 --> 00:20:35,300
That's why I'm trying to secure
our interests here.

486
00:20:35,300 --> 00:20:35,900
Wait.

487
00:20:36,580 --> 00:20:38,940
Our family helped out
in decorating the house

488
00:20:38,940 --> 00:20:39,890
and the children's room.

489
00:20:39,900 --> 00:20:41,100
Isn't that good enough?

490
00:20:41,210 --> 00:20:43,100
Must you talk about
such materialistic things...

491
00:20:43,100 --> 00:20:44,540
Enough.

492
00:20:47,020 --> 00:20:49,300
We should keep our promise.

493
00:20:51,980 --> 00:20:54,140
Mingzhu, go and perform the procedure.

494
00:20:54,460 --> 00:20:56,050
We'll do our best to cooperate with you.

495
00:20:56,660 --> 00:20:57,500
Thank you, Dad.

496
00:20:59,820 --> 00:21:00,700
I'll head to work now.

497
00:21:05,500 --> 00:21:06,060
Let's eat.

498
00:21:14,860 --> 00:21:15,860
That was too hasty.

499
00:21:16,960 --> 00:21:18,860
You told your parents-in-law that you
wanted to do an ownership transfer,

500
00:21:18,860 --> 00:21:20,120
and they actually agreed to it?

501
00:21:21,620 --> 00:21:23,940
But I offended
my mother-in-law and Meiqi again.

502
00:21:24,700 --> 00:21:26,140
That's fine.

503
00:21:26,140 --> 00:21:28,240
If you don't offend them,
you'll swallow grievances.

504
00:21:29,540 --> 00:21:31,020
Yesterday, I saw my father-in-law's

505
00:21:31,020 --> 00:21:32,180
Alipay account.

506
00:21:32,480 --> 00:21:33,940
He only has a few hundred yuan left.

507
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:36,660
I was wondering if his company
is facing some sort of trouble.

508
00:21:39,140 --> 00:21:40,060
It won't be that bad.

509
00:21:42,140 --> 00:21:43,900
Anyway, I want to help my child

510
00:21:44,260 --> 00:21:45,700
to hold on to everything

511
00:21:45,700 --> 00:21:46,820
that I can grasp in my hand.

512
00:21:50,980 --> 00:21:52,860
Am I being too selfish?

513
00:21:53,820 --> 00:21:55,140
How is this selfish?

514
00:21:55,160 --> 00:21:56,420
You're doing this for your child.

515
00:21:56,420 --> 00:21:57,580
It's not selfish at all.

516
00:21:57,590 --> 00:21:58,680
Besides, your parents-in-law

517
00:21:58,690 --> 00:22:00,220
already promised to give you the house.

518
00:22:00,220 --> 00:22:00,780
Am I right?

519
00:22:00,860 --> 00:22:02,620
It's time for them
to keep their promise.

520
00:22:02,820 --> 00:22:03,980
I suppose you could say that.

521
00:22:04,820 --> 00:22:06,260
Anyway, my mother-in-law and Meiqi

522
00:22:06,260 --> 00:22:07,460
were quite upset.

523
00:22:09,500 --> 00:22:10,740
Meiqi is upset, huh?

524
00:22:12,260 --> 00:22:12,900
Oh no.

525
00:22:12,900 --> 00:22:13,620
What's wrong?

526
00:22:13,660 --> 00:22:15,440
Will it affect her
from being Bichen's bridesmaid?

527
00:22:22,180 --> 00:22:22,900
Please sign here.

528
00:22:23,220 --> 00:22:23,660
Okay.

529
00:22:23,660 --> 00:22:28,300
(Real Estate Registration)

530
00:22:31,360 --> 00:22:31,900
Here you go.

531
00:22:33,980 --> 00:22:34,620
Keep it well.

532
00:22:35,700 --> 00:22:36,380
Is that all?

533
00:22:36,380 --> 00:22:36,980
Yes.

534
00:22:36,980 --> 00:22:37,540
Okay.

535
00:22:37,620 --> 00:22:39,260
(People's Republic of China
Real Estate Ownership Certificate)

536
00:22:39,460 --> 00:22:40,100
Here.

